---
// Componente Sobre Mi - Ruth Esther
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
import IconExcel from '../assets/svg/IconExcel.svg?raw'
import IconPython from '../assets/svg/IconPython.svg?raw'
import IconMssql from '../assets/svg/IconMssql.svg?raw'
import IconPowerbi from '../assets/svg/IconPowerbi.svg?raw'
---

<Layout title="Sobre Mí | Ruth Esther" description="Portafolio profesional de Ruth Esther, Data Analyst.">
    <section id="sobre-mi" class="p-6 md:p-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-transparent">
     <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
       
       <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
         <h3 data-translate_key="about_me_profile_title" class="text-2xl font-bold text-tm-pr border-b-2 border-tm-pr w-fit pb-1">
           My profile
         </h3>
         <p data-translate_key="about_me_profile_text" class="text-lg card p-4 text-tm-text2 leading-relaxed animate-fade-in">
            Data Analyst with solid experience in <b class="text-tm-pr">ETL</b> processes, <b class="text-tm-pr">dynamic dashboard</b> creation, and database management using
            <b class="text-tm-pr">DDL</b> and <b class="text-tm-pr">DML</b>, as well as designing <b class="text-tm-pr">performance KPIs</b> to evaluate operational efficiency. My focus is on transforming complex data 
            into strategic information that drives organizational growth.
            With a background in <b class="text-tm-pr">Software Development</b>, I combine programming logic with statistical analysis to deliver
            precise and scalable solutions.
         </p>
       </div>
   
       <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
         <h3 data-translate_key="about_me_tools_title" class="text-2xl font-bold text-tm-pr border-b-2 border-tm-pr w-fit pb-1">
           Tools and expertise
         </h3>
         <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
           
           <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-tm-bg-50 border border-tm-pr/10 hover:border-tm-pr transition-all animate-fade-in">
             <div class="w-8 h-8 text-tm-pr shrink-0" set:html={IconExcel} />
             <div>
               <h4 data-translate_key="about_me_excel" class="font-bold text-tm-se leading-none mb-1">Advanced Excel</h4>
               <p data-translate_key="about_me_excel_text" class="text-xs text-tm-text2">Macros, Pivot Tables, Dashboards, Visual Basic, Complex Data Analysis, and Financial Modeling.</p>
             </div>
           </div>
   
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-tm-bg-50 border border-tm-pr/10 hover:border-tm-pr transition-all min-h-[100px] animate-fade-in">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 text-tm-pr shrink-0" set:html={IconMssql} />
                <div class="overflow-hidden">
                  <h4 data-translate_key="about_me_sql" class="font-bold text-tm-se leading-tight mb-1">SQL Server</h4>
                  <p data-translate_key="about_me_sql_text" class="text-xs text-tm-text2">DML/DDL management, optimized queries, and data architecture.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
   
           <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-tm-bg-50 border border-tm-pr/10 hover:border-tm-pr transition-all animate-fade-in">
             <div class="w-8 h-8 text-tm-pr shrink-0" set:html={IconPowerbi} />
             <div>
               <h4 data-translate_key="about_me_powerbi" class="font-bold text-tm-se leading-none mb-1">Power BI</h4>
               <p data-translate_key="about_me_powerbi_text" class="text-xs text-tm-text2">Real-time KPI dashboards, data visualization, and interactive report creation.</p>
             </div>
           </div>
   
           <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl bg-tm-bg-50 border border-tm-pr/10 hover:border-tm-pr transition-all animate-fade-in">
             <div class="w-8 h-8 text-tm-pr shrink-0" set:html={IconPython} />
             <div>
               <h4 data-translate_key="about_me_python" class="font-bold text-tm-se leading-none mb-1">Python (Pandas)</h4>
               <p data-translate_key="about_me_python_text" class="text-xs text-tm-text2">Large-scale data cleaning, task automation, and logic development.</p>
             </div>
           </div>
         </div>
       </div>
   
       <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
         <div class="flex-1">
           <h3 data-translate_key="about_me_language_title" class="text-2xl font-bold text-tm-pr border-b-2 border-tm-pr w-fit pb-1 mb-4">
             Languages
           </h3>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
             <span data-translate_key="about_me_spanish" class="font-bold text-tm-se uppercase">Spanish:</span>
             <span data-translate_key="about_me_spanish_val" class="px-3 py-1 bg-tm-pr/10 text-tm-pr rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Native</span>
           </div>
           <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
             <span data-translate_key="about_me_english" class="font-bold text-tm-se uppercase">English:</span>
             <span data-translate_key="about_me_english_val" class="px-3 py-1 bg-tm-pr/10 text-tm-pr rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Intermediate Level</span>
           </div>
         </div>
   
         <div class="flex-1">
           <h3 data-translate_key="about_me_vision" class="text-2xl font-bold text-tm-pr border-b-2 border-tm-pr w-fit pb-1 mb-4">
               Vision and Purpose
           </h3>
           <p data-translate_key="about_me_vision_text" class="card p-4 text-tm-text2 leading-relaxed animate-fade-in">
             My driving force is <b class="text-tm-pr">constant evolution</b>. I don't just seek to analyze data, but to master new technologies that allow me to predict the
             future of business. I am passionate about self-taught learning and my goal is to become a leader in <b class="text-tm-pr">Data Science</b>, providing disruptive solutions
             that break with the conventional in high-performance environments.
           </p>
         </div>
       </div>
     </div>
   </section>
</Layout>
